## Acceptance Criteria
- `ensureDefaultTemplates()` creates 4 template `.md` files on first run
- Templates are idempotent (second run is no-op if any .md files exist)
- `loadTemplates()` reads and parses template files
- Old presets code is removed
- Templates are seeded at `{dorkHome}/tasks/templates/`
